---
// About section — bio and skills
---

<div class="mb-16">
  <h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-accent mb-8">// about</h2>
  <p class="text-text-primary leading-relaxed mb-4">
    Hi, my name is Micah Ice. I'm a high school developer who specializes in
    building apps and tools. This is a collection of my apps and projects that
    I've been building since January 2026. If you're interested in learning how
    to build your own apps or wish to hire me as your developer{' '}
    <a
      href="#contact"
      class="email-cta inline-flex items-baseline font-mono text-sm text-accent border border-accent px-2 py-0.5 rounded transition-colors duration-150 hover:bg-accent hover:text-bg"
    >
      <span class="bracket text-accent-alt mr-1">[</span>
      <span>email me</span>
      <span class="caret ml-0.5">_</span>
      <span class="bracket text-accent-alt ml-1">]</span>
    </a>{' '}
    below.
  </p>
  <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-6">
    {['17 Years Old', 'Entrepreneur', 'High School Developer', 'App Builder', 'Self-Taught'].map((skill) => (
      <span class="text-xs font-mono text-accent-alt border border-border px-3 py-1 rounded">
        {skill}
      </span>
    ))}
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .email-cta .caret {
    animation: email-cta-blink 0.9s step-end infinite;
  }

  .email-cta:hover .bracket {
    color: inherit;
  }

  @keyframes email-cta-blink {
    from, to { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0; }
  }
</style>
